      "text": "# Brain 2.0 Architecture"
    },
    {
      "id": "raw-sources",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 0,
      "y": 20,
      "width": 280,
      "height": 200,
      "color": "4",
      "text": "## Layer 1: Raw Sources\n*Immutable \u2014 LLM reads, never modifies*\n\n- `standups/` transcripts\n- `scopes/*/spec.md`\n- `marty/memory/*.md`\n- `docs/plans/`\n- Slack threads\n- Customer interviews"
    },
    {
      "id": "wiki",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 360,
      "y": 20,
      "width": 280,
      "height": 200,
      "color": "5",
      "text": "## Layer 2: The Wiki\n*LLM-maintained \u2014 Jake reads*\n\n- `shared/*.md` (state, missions, gotchas)\n- `shared/INDEX.md` (routing)\n- `shared/log.md` (timeline)\n- `marty/wiki/*.md` (intelligence)\n- `memory/*.md` (per-session)"
    },
    {
      "id": "schema",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 720,
      "y": 20,
      "width": 280,
      "height": 200,
      "color": "1",
      "text": "## Layer 3: The Schema\n*Co-evolved \u2014 tells LLM how to maintain*\n\n- `CLAUDE.md` (global rules)\n- `shared/brain.md` (philosophy)\n- `marty/AGENTS.md` (Marty\u2019s schema)\n- `~/.claude/commands/` (operations)"
    },
    {
      "id": "ingest",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 80,
      "y": 300,
      "width": 200,
      "height": 80,
      "color": "6",
      "text": "### Ingest\n`/brain-compile`\n`/compound`\nMarty post-standup"
    },
    {
      "id": "query",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 400,
      "y": 300,
      "width": 200,
      "height": 80,
      "color": "6",
      "text": "### Query\nNormal Claude sessions\nGood answers filed back"
    },
    {
      "id": "lint",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 720,
      "y": 300,
      "width": 200,
      "height": 80,
      "color": "6",
      "text": "### Lint\n`/brain-lint`\nMarty Friday cron\nHealth score tracking"
    },
    {
      "id": "loop",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 300,
      "y": 440,
      "width": 400,
      "height": 60,
      "color": "3",
      "text": "**Compounding Loop:** Ingest makes it richer \u2192 Query makes it smarter \u2192 Lint makes it healthier"
    }
  ],
